Key Match Events: Virat Kohli scored 95 runs off 104 balls.
Mohammed Shami took 5 wickets for 54 runs.
Daryl Mitchell scored 130 runs off 127 balls.
India won by 4 wickets with 12 balls remaining.
Miscellaneous Highlights: India won the toss and elected to field first.
The match was held at Himachal Pradesh Cricket Association Stadium, Dharamsala.
Mohammed Shami was named Player of the Match.
